title: Sonic the Hedgehog (Archie Comics)
description:
The fuck even happens in Archie Sonic? A lot, apparently.

This is a compilation of basically every single Archie Sonic story, including the main book issues, Knuckles the Echidina, Sonic Universe, mini-series, specials and additional crossovers. Scans were sourced from a mixture of Internet Archive uploads, [grabber.zone](grabber.zone), tails-kicks-ass scans and [Hollie Taylor's](https://bsky.app/profile/hollietaylor.bsky.social) collection, in particular the remastered/color corrected scans for the first 62ish issues.

Optimal reading order taken from [Thanks Ken Penders](https://thankskenpenders.tumblr.com/readingorder) you should check it in case you don't want read every single item here (understandably)

If there's a problem with any of the chapters please create an issue in the Easy Archie Sonic project github: [https://github.com/SkywayOctane/Easy-Archie-Sonic](https://github.com/SkywayOctane/Easy-Archie-Sonic)
